OL,5,G0405 Bradley & Barney Walsh: Breaking
OL,6,G     Dad
OL,7,     FBefore they leave the Blue
OL,8,     FMountains, Barney has an extreme
OL,9,     Fchallenge planned for his dad as
OL,10,     Fthey must traverse a ravine on a
OL,11,     Frope. The men then head to the
OL,12,     Fcountryside and make a stop in the
OL,13,     Fland of sheep, where they learn
OL,14,     Fthe art of shearing. Later, the
OL,15,     Froad trip takes them to a tiny
OL,16,     Ftown where they join the local
OL,17,     Fcommunity who have organised a
OL,18,     Fchallenge that involves pulling a
OL,19,     Fgigantic truck
